Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.63,0:22:29.26,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}悪い夢に溺れた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.26,0:22:31.92,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}のどが渴いて目覚めた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.92,0:22:37.18,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}これはいつの記憶なんだったっけ?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.18,0:22:44.03,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}誰かを忘れている気がしてまた眠る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.80,0:22:50.10,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}子供のふりをして
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.92,0:22:55.66,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}背伸びで盾になりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.66,0:23:00.60,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}手を取り合えばあたたかくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.93,0:23:05.83,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}抱きしめ合えばやわらかくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.22,0:23:08.21,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}約束しよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.21,0:23:15.54,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}「わたしたち」をずっと続けるって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.72,0:23:22.09,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}この先何も起こらないように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.09,0:23:27.06,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}邪魔者なんて入らないように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:33.81,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}大切な人を大切にしたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.81,0:23:41.22,ED - JP,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}オリジナルの誓い口ずさんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.63,0:22:29.26,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}淹沒於噩夢中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.26,0:22:31.92,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}因口渴而甦醒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.92,0:22:37.18,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}這是何時的記憶來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.18,0:22:44.03,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}感覺遺忘了某人  再次沉沉睡去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.80,0:22:50.10,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}像個孩子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.92,0:22:55.66,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}勉強自己守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.66,0:23:00.60,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}一起攜手共進是如此溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.93,0:23:05.83,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}一起相擁偎依是如此柔軟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.22,0:23:08.21,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}許下約定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.21,0:23:15.54,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}要將「我們」一直延續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.72,0:23:22.09,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}願前路一帆風順
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.09,0:23:27.06,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}願未來暢行無礙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:33.81,ED - CN,,0,0,0,,{\1a&HFF&\blur6\bord4\fad(200,200)}想守護珍視之人
